node.text: Our first Instagram Live with our co-founder & CCO Anna Bond! She talks about our founding, answers questions, shared favorite products and give sneak peeks at upcoming goods.

node.text: Bring home some flowers with our illustrated art prints, 25% off during our End of Summer Sale 🌷🌻🌺 (Sale excludes wallpaper and swim) #riflepaperco

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Rifle Paper Co. on September 01, 2021 tagging @annariflebond, and @riflepaperco. May be an image of text.

node.text: We’re wrapping up summer with a sale! Take 25% off sitewide starting now on riflepaperco.com 🌼❤️✨ (Sale is in our Winter Park store and online, *excludes wallpaper and swim) #riflepaperco
